{"tid":1586140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當日200萬香港人 抖完未?","createTime":"2019-09-21T20:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T07:15:23.000Z","uid":3431,"like":69,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"6842ad2e900f0c11c7d62e19323c0cbd31f60c4c","tid":1586140,"uid":3431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T20:51:11.000Z","msg":"抖夠就出返嚟啦 自從616之後嘅抗爭<br />\n人數都未夠當時 818算多 但喺唔夠呀<br />\n喺咪唔記得咗中共最叻乜嘢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">秋後算帳</span> 4隻字仲識架可?<br />\n點解每次popo 都拎住個cam 影住<br />\n就喺等場運動散撚咗 就慢慢促9你<br />\n今時今日仲唔企出街 唔好之後怨天尤人<br />\n唔好話香港無自由 唔好話無民主<br />\n一切掌決於你今日嘅選擇決定而造成<br />\n<br />\n唔好再打飛機話等解放軍入港攬炒經濟<br />\n我想問一句<span style=\"color: red;\"> 一件popo 衫好撚貴?</span><br />\n擺撚明唔show number架啦 唔洗再問委任證<br />\n因為一張證都唔值錢 我意思唔喺叫你地習慣<br />\n而喺我地應該要一齊諗有咩方法 拎到證據證明<br />\n再放上國際 咁樣先喺可行 連登已經好多打手<br />\n有時間 推下行動post 推下值得嘅post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">今日辛苦各位 未完 再加油!<br />\n場仗唔可以輸 輸咗 玩撚完!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">光復香港 時候革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人 抖夠拿 要埋位</span></span>"},{"pid":"fc89128dbd772bac23bc69f4f2591e8816105cd2","tid":1586140,"uid":3431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T20:51:23.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"f8304ee0ec07a6b5a73ea7a4c55e17c257d224a9","tid":1586140,"uid":3431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T20:51:58.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"1c1a1f6b5b6d329f2223c94ac4bc5381879bdbfc","tid":1586140,"uid":3431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T20:52:09.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"a9fdcebed79aea496c3d178be7b4c3ed6ddc1592","tid":1586140,"uid":3431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T20:52:19.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"8a35f2bb308737c7